data.description: WELCOME TO YOUR DREAM HOME IN ALLEN, TEXAS! No HOA! Upgraded STEEL ROOF!  This 5 bed, 3.5 bath, 3,370sf home is east facing with easy access to Rt. 75, shopping, parks, and amenities. With the primary bedroom on the first floor and the remaining four bedrooms located on the second, everyone will have space to relax and unwind. As you step inside, you'll be captivated by the grandeur and spaciousness of this home. Two cozy fireplaces add a touch of warmth and elegance to your gatherings. Step outside to your own personal oasis, complete with a refreshing pool and a soothing hot tub. The low-maintenance backyard ensures that your outdoor space is as enjoyable as it is hassle-free. Allen, Texas offers an array of amenities with shopping, restaurants and parks close by. With its proximity to Route 75 commuting is simplified. Don't miss the opportunity to make this residence your forever home, where grand living spaces and a prime location create the ultimate lifestyle experience.
